    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<h1>WACHUNGAJI</h1><p>Wanaume waliowatunza wanyama wa nyumbani, kama vile ng&apos;ombe, kondoo na mbuzi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:7-Gen13:8\">Mwanzo 13:7–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:20\">26:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam21:7\">1&nbsp;Samweli 21:7</a>), pia walijumuisha wachungaji wa kondoo. Katika Agano Jipya, wachungaji wa kondoo walikuwa maarufu sana. Mfano wa mchungaji wa kondoo na kondoo wake ulitumiwa na Yesu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:1-John10:16\">Yohana 10:1–16</a>). Baadhi ya wachungaji walifuga nguruwe (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:33\">Mathayo 8:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:14\">Marko 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:34\">Luka 8:34</a>).</p>",
